<Weakness xmlns="http://cwe.mitre.org/cwe-7" xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" ID="522" Name="Insufficiently Protected Credentials" Abstraction="Class" Structure="Simple" Status="Incomplete">
         <Description>The product transmits or stores authentication credentials, but it uses an insecure method that is susceptible to unauthorized interception and/or retrieval.</Description>
